name: Paula Agyiri
description: I am a very open minded person, someone who accepts people as they are, I am a fair individual who adapts to changes in life and enjoys life to the fullest, and looking to meet a man that i can spend the rest of my life with in good time and in bad times as well, A man that I can love and cherished with all my whole being and heart and I pray to God almighty that he will provide me with that kind of a man someday in my life, I’m pride of myself in being honest and most trustworthy, I seek that in a mate, someone who is compassionate yet understanding who has a calm behavior and a great personality.
